"guardian" of a person under a legal disability
includes&#8212;
         (a)     a trustee who holds property on trust for the person under an
instrument of trust or direction of a court or tribunal;
         (b)     an administrator for the person appointed in an administration order
made under the Guardianship and Administration Act 2019;
